<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #007bff; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .info-box { background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .warning { background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>You're Invited to MRDBID</h2>

      <p>Hello,</p>

      <p>You've been invited to join MRDBID with <strong>full admin access for 24 hours</strong>. We value your expertise and would love your help advancing our mushroom character identification system.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <strong>Getting Started:</strong><br>
        Simply click the button below to instantly access the site with full admin privileges. No signup, no password, no hassle.
      </div>

      <center>
        <a href="<%= @magic_link %>" class="button">Access MRDBID Now</a>
      </center>

      <div class="warning">
        <strong>Important Information:</strong><br>
        • Your admin access expires <%= distance_of_time_in_words_to_now(@expires_at) %> from now<br>
        • After expiration, you'll be automatically downgraded to read-only access<br>
        • To continue as a permanent admin, simply create a regular account on the site and email <strong>will@mrdbid.com</strong> to request permanent admin privileges
      </div>

      <p>We're excited to have your contributions!</p>

      <p>
        Best regards,<br>
        The MRDBID Team
      </p>

      <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;">

      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
        If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
        <%= @magic_link %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
